Use Case:
Creating a Bill
Trigger:
The car garage wants to create a billing software management 
Preconditions:


Main scenarios:


1-
The customer specifies his personal details.
2-
The receptionist enters the details into the system.
3-
The customer specifies the services he wants.
4-
The mechanic start doing the services. 
5-
The receptionist enter the services into the system
6-
The system displays the amount of each service.
7-
The system includes taxes and discounts.
8- 
The system creates the bill with all the information.
9-
The receptionist will give the bill to the customer.
Exceptions:


3a
1-The services are not available.
2-The customer chooses a different service  
6a
1-The customer might not have a discount.

